<p><strong>The Pachakuti Mesa Tradition</strong> is a system that utilizes an altar like arrangement called a mesa¬†at its core¬†yet emphasizes the flexibility, the cultural context, and the creative potential of each apprentice in a way <strong>that transforms not only their lives, but also the planet.</strong></p>

